author: Andrew O'Reilly
title: Whitmer defends stay-at-home orders amid protests; says coronavirus is 'disproportionately hurting' Michigan
description: Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer continued on Sunday to defend her updated stay-at-home orders to battle the coronavirus pandemic despite facing large protests from residents eager to get out of their houses.
